English Corner – PRIVACY POLICY
INTRODUCTION
Welcome to English Corner! English Corner is the social networking platform on SMARTRAY STUDIO English leraning apps - English Radio, AEB and English Corner.
Smartray Studio.
("
we
", "
our
" or "
us
") values your privacy.
          This Privacy Policy informs you of your choices and our practices
          regarding any Information (as defined in the "The Information We
