The use of English Corner (through the English Corner mobile app, or
          any third party platforms through which English Corner is provided)
          may involve the collection and use of your Information. It is
          important for you to understand how this happens and how you may
          control it, so please read this Privacy Policy carefully.
By using English Corner, you agree that we may collect, use and
            share your Information in accordance with this Privacy Policy, as
            revised from time to time.
If you wish to contact us regarding this Privacy Policy or any
          privacy-related matters, please contact our Privacy Officer via email
