SCOPE AND APPLICATION OF THIS PRIVACY POLICY
This Privacy Policy applies to English Corner, including any services
          associated with English Corner that incorporates this Privacy Policy
          by reference (for example, the English Corner Official Account Admin
          Platform). Those English Corner-related services may have further
          privacy-related terms that you must agree to as part of your use of
          those services.
This Privacy Policy is incorporated into and forms part of the
English Corner Terms of Service
that you have agreed to in order to use English Corner. Any terms used
          in this Privacy Policy will have the same meaning as the equivalent
          defined terms in the
English Corner Terms of Service
, unless
          otherwise defined in this Privacy Policy or the context requires
          otherwise.
Please also note that this Privacy Policy does not apply to
          Information collected: (i) through third party services (including any
          third party websites) that you may access through English Corner; or
          (ii) by other companies and organisations who advertise their services
          on English Corner.
CHANGES TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY
We may from time to time revise or add specific instructions, policies
          and terms to this Privacy Policy. These instructions, policies and
          terms form part of this Privacy Policy. Where we consider that any
          changes to this Privacy Policy are reasonably material, we will notify
          you via English Corner (including via direct messaging or the English
          Corner website), other direct communication to you, or other means
          prior to the change becoming effective.
By continuing to use English Corner after any changes to this
            Privacy Policy, with or without notice from us,you are agreeing to
            the revised Privacy Policy.
THE INFORMATION WE COLLECT AND HOW WE COLLECT IT
In providing English Corner, we collect, store and use the following
          Information relating to you:
"
Information
" is Personal Information and
          Non-Personal Information;
"
Personal Information
" is any information or
          combination of information that relates to you, and can be used to
          identify you. Personal Information may include the following:
information you make available to us when you open a English Corner
            account, such as your email address, nickname, photo, country/area and
            other information you put on your public profile;
information you make available to us via your use of English Corner
            – for example, via: Public Blogs and Moments for your friends;
information made available by another user about you via their use
            of English Corner – for example, any Shared Information that others
            using English Corner make available about you via English Corner
            Moments and communications they make to you and others using English
            Corner;
information we collect as you use English Corner, such as certain
            Location Data and Log Data.
"
Location Data
" is information that we collect
          regarding your location (when you use a location-enabled service),
          including:
the location of your device when you use English Corner, such as
            from the GPS, WiFi, compass, accelerometer or other sensors in your
            mobile device;
the IP address of the device or internet service you use to access
            English Corner;
other information made available by you or others that gives an
            indication as to where you are or have been located, such as account
            information that indicates where you are located, and Shared
            Information that you or others post which indicates your location
            (for example, any geotag information that is embedded in any photos
            you make available on English Corner or that is made available to us
            when you use the English Corner "People Nearby" functions).
"
Log Data
" is technical information that is
          automatically collected by us when you use English Corner, whether
          through the use of cookies, web beacons, log files, scripts and etags
          (as explained in more detail in the "Tracking Technologies" section
          below) or otherwise, including:
technical information, such as your mobile carrier-related
            information, configuration information made available by your web
            browser or other programs you use to access app website, your IP
            address and your device's version and identification number;
information about communications you have made using English Corner,
            such as the people you've communicated with and the time, data and
            duration of your communications;
metadata, which means information related to items you have made
            available through English Corner, such as the date, time or location
            that a shared photograph or video was taken or posted.
"
Non-Personal Information
" is any information that
          relates to you but from which it is not practicable to directly or
          indirectly identify you, including Personal Information in aggregated,
          anonymised or pseudonymised form.
"
Shared Information
" is information about you or
          relating to you that is voluntarily shared on English Corner. Shared
          Information may include postings that you make on English Corner
          (including your public profile, the lists you create, and photos,
          videos and voice recordings as accessed with your prior consent
          through your device's camera and/or microphone sensor), any postings
          from others that you re-post and Location Data and Log Data associated
          with such postings. Shared Information also includes information about
          you (including Location Data and Log Data) that others who are using
          our services share about you.
HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION
We may use your Information for any of the following purposes:
to provide English Corner (and the features within English Corner)
            to you – for example, to allow you to record audio or videos within
            English Corner, to fulfil any purchases you may make within English
            Corner, and to display content based on your location or your preferences;
for customer service, security, fraud-detection, archival and backup
            purposes in connection with the provision of English Corner;
to provide you with advertising and direct marketing that is more
            relevant to you (as discussed in more detail below under the "Direct
            Marketing" section below);
to better understand how you access and use English Corner, in order
            for us to improve English Corner and respond to customer desires and
            preferences, including for us to provide language and location
            customisation, personalised help and instructions, or other
            responses to your and other customers' usage of English Corner;
to help us develop our new services and improve our existing
            services;
to assess the effectiveness of and improve advertising and other
            marketing and promotional activities on or in connection with
            English Corner when your account is subscribed to an official
            account;
to allow you to participate in voluntary surveys about our products
            and services. If you choose to participate in a survey, we may
            request certain Personal Information from you. We may use a third
            party service provider to conduct these surveys; we will prohibit
            them from using your Personal Information for any purpose other than
            to complete the survey.
Use of Personal Information on our other services
In order to provide our users across all of our services with a better
          experience, to improve English Corner and our other services, or
          otherwise where you have consented, Personal Information collected
          through English Corner may, subject to user privacy controls (where
          available), be used by our other services (including in an aggregated
          or individualised manner).
For example, Personal Information collected during your use of English
          Corner may be used to suggest particular content that can be made
          available to you on, or be used to present more relevant advertising
          to you in, another Smartray service. You may also ask us to migrate or
          export your Personal Information contained in English Corner to
          another Smartray service, where such migration option is available.
DIRECT MARKETING
We may also use your Information for the purpose of sending you direct
          marketing (whether by messaging within our services, by email or by
          other means) that offer or advertise our products and services and/or
          the products and services of selected third parties.
Such products and services (of ours or third parties) include the
          following:
our products and services and the products and services of our
            joint venture partners,
            including messaging services, online media services, interactive
            entertainment services, social networking services, payment
            services, internet search services, location and mapping services,
            application software and services, data management software and
            services, on-line advertising services and other social media,
            entertainment, e-commerce, information and communications software
            and services ("
Internet Services
"); and
third party providers of Internet Services and products and services
            relating to dining, food and beverages, sports, music, film,
            television, live performances and other arts and entertainment,
            books, magazines and other publications, clothing and accessories,
            jewellery, cosmetics, personal health and hygiene, electronics,
            collectibles, housewares, appliances, home decoration and
            furnishings, pets, automobiles, hotels, transport and travel,
            banking, insurance and financial services, loyalty and reward
            programs and other products and services that we think may be
            relevant to you.
We will honour your request for us to not use your Personal
          Information for the direct marketing purposes noted above. If you wish
          to make such a request, please contact our Privacy Officer or follow
          the relevant instructions on our marketing communications. Please note
          that following such request, you may still receive advertisements that
          are not direct marketing.
Please note that we will not share your Personal Information with
          advertisers. We do,
          however, share Non-Personal Information with advertisers for the
          purposes of trying to offer you advertising that is more relevant to
          you.
SHARING OF YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION
By agreeing to this Privacy Policy, you consent to the third party
            use, sharing and transfer of your Personal Information (both inside
            and outside of your jurisdiction) as described in this section.
            Other than as permitted under this Privacy Policy or as otherwise
            consented to by you, we will not transfer your Personal Information
            to any other third parties for their processing for any
            purposes.
Sharing for marketing purposes
In addition, we allow third party marketing partners (such as English
          Corner official accounts, analytics providers and advertising
          partners) to collect your Personal Information over time and across
          different websites or online services when you use English Corner.
We also provide your Personal Information to third party marketing
          partners where you have asked us to do so or where it is required in
          order for us to provide English Corner to you.
Other terms relating to the sharing of your Personal
            Information
Where we do share your Personal Information
          with any third parties, we will use reasonable efforts to ensure that
          such third parties only use your Personal Information: (i) in
          compliance with this Privacy Policy; and (ii) subject to any other
          instructions we give them, including any appropriate confidentiality
          and security measures that we implement.
As we continue to develop our business, we or our affiliate companies
          may be acquired by a third party or may re-organise our group
          structure. In these circumstances, your Information may be transferred
          within our group and/or to a third party who will continue to operate
          English Corner or similar services under either this Privacy Policy or
          a different privacy policy which will be notified to you. The party to
          which your Personal Information is transferred may be located, and use
          your Information, outside of your jurisdiction.
Any of the above-referenced third parties in this "Sharing of your
          Personal Information" section may be located, and use and store your
          Personal Information, outside of your jurisdiction for the above
          purposes, including in jurisdictions where there may not be in place
          data protection laws that are substantially similar to or serve the
          same purpose as the laws of your jurisdiction.
We may also be required to retain, preserve or disclose your Personal
          Information under the circumstances set out in the "Period of use of
          your Personal Information" section below.
A WORD ABOUT SHARED INFORMATION
English Corner enables Shared Information to be shared publicly with
          your English Corner contacts, all users of English Corner and/or the
          public, via features provided by either us or third parties, so that
          Shared Information can be broadly and instantly transmitted. Shared
          Information will remain public for as long as you do not delete it;
          and even after you delete Shared Information, it may still be
          separately cached, copied, or stored by, or remain public through,
          other users or third parties who are not affiliated with and not
          controlled by us.
In addition, we may also provide other English Corner-related features
          that allow you to share Shared Information in public – for example,
          publicly accessible blogs and forums, or certain social media features
          within English Corner – for example, "plug-ins" (which create a direct
          link between two websites) and "widgets" (which are interactive
          mini-programs that provide third party services within English
          Corner). You should be aware that any information you provide within
          such features may be read, collected and used by third parties who
          access them.
Please consider carefully what you post and communicate through
            English Corner.
In some instances, you may control what access the wider public has to
          your Shared Information via the privacy settings in some of English
          Corner.
UPDATING OR AMENDING YOUR PERSONAL INFORMATION
If you would like to update or amend your Personal Information within
          English Corner, you may do so at first instance by logging into your
          account and making the appropriate changes. For example, you may be
          able to delete certain Location Data that you have provided us via
          your device settings or the "Disable Location" option within English
          Corner.
If you wish to make further changes to your Personal Information;
          request access to, or deletion of, your Personal Information from
          English Corner; or to request the removal of an unauthorised English
          Corner account, please contact us. We will respond to
          your request within a reasonable timeframe.
In some cases, we may not be able to update, amend or remove your
          Personal Information, in which case we will let you know why we are
          unable to do so – for example, certain requests may require
          disproportionate technical effort or extremely impractical (e.g. any
          requests that relate to our backup systems), or are prohibited by law.
HOW CAN I DELETE INFORMATION ABOUT ME?
You can delete your data in app or request us to delete your data. The data includes your personal data and all the things that you have shared, 
      including your albums, photos, blogs, moments and chat history. Please note that once this process is complete, your Personal Data will be deleted and we will no longer collect, use and/or disclose your Personal Data,
      and there is no way to recover them.
      Please refer to the following information on how to proceed.
* Deleting your Account
To delete your account, please go to App > Settings > Member Center > Delete My Account.
* Other requests to delete your personal data
You could also request that we delete your data by sending an email to
SmartrayStudio@gmail.com
.
